IN RE the DEPENDENCY OF: G.L., Petitioner. No. 95341-4 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, March 7, 2018.

ORDER

¶ 1 Department I of the Court, composed of Chief Justice Fairhurst and Justices Johnson, Owens, Wiggins, and Gordon McCloud, considered this matter at its March 6, 2018, Motion Calendar and unanimously agreed that the following order be entered.

¶ 2 IT IS ORDERED:

¶ 3 That the Petitioner's motion for discretionary review and the motion for extraordinary relief are both denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J.

CHIEF JUSTICE
